folder: Surf Ave. & 17th St. W., Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1)
Surf Ave., west side, east of West 17th Street.
January 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, slightly eastward, showiwg in the background Loew's Coney Island Theatre building under construction, at the N.W. corner of Stillwell and Surf Aves.
December 31, 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(3)
The same, showing the building completed.
June 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
